OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FMore vehicles were clamped in Cardiff
OL,7,Flast year than in bigger UK cities
OL,8,Flike Glasgow, Edinburgh, Bristol and
OL,9,FSheffield.
OL,11,FIn fact, the Welsh capital saw the
OL,12,Ffourth highest number of clamping
OL,13,Factions in any UK city, behind only
OL,14,FLondon, Manchester and Birmingham.
OL,16,FThe reason? Failure to pay Vehicle
OL,17,FExcise Duty, otherwise known as road
OL,18,Ftax.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
