FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FAll cars registered in the UK and
OL,7,Fdriven on public roads must register
OL,8,Ffor this tax but how much you pay
OL,9,Fdepends on your vehicle. There are
OL,10,Falso some exemptions for people living
OL,11,Fwith disabilities or owners of
OL,12,Fvehicles older than 40 years.
OL,14,FThe DVLA says roughly one in every 100
OL,15,Fcars on the road is untaxed. Catching
OL,16,Fthem requires ANPR fitted vehicles,
OL,17,Fmeaning patrol cars with cameras that
OL,18,Fcan read number plates and check them
OL,19,Fagainst a database.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
