CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FWe were invited by the DVLA to follow
OL,7,Fone of their patrols with wheel
OL,8,Fclamping operators in Newport. For
OL,9,Fpersonal safety reasons none of them
OL,10,Fwanted to be identified. The DVLA says
OL,11,Faggressive or threatening behaviour
OL,12,Ftowards its staff is rare but not
OL,13,Funheard of.
OL,15,FPaul Davies is the DVLA's Senior
OL,16,FLeader for National Wheelclamping &
OL,17,FANPR Enforcement. Driving around
OL,18,FNewport, I asked him whether they were
OL,19,Fseeing an increase in bad attitudes
OL,20,Ftowards his staff by drivers who have
OL,21,Fnot paid the tax.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,F"For those who get caught, yes," he
OL,7,Fsaid. "But a lot of the public are
OL,8,Fvery supportive of the action we take,
OL,9,Fespecially because most people pay
OL,10,Ftheir tax.
OL,12,F"We normally get requests from people
OL,13,Fsaying can you come to our area and
OL,14,Fhelp with some of the untaxed vehicles
OL,15,Fthat are being a nuisance and open to
OL,16,Fantisocial behaviour.
OL,18,F"The ones who get caught are not so
OL,19,Fhappy."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FIn a new ad campaign for 2026, the
OL,7,FDVLA feature a down-on-his-luck
OL,8,Ftalking wheelclamp called 'Clampy'. In
OL,9,Fone ad he is being urinated on by a
OL,10,Fpassing dog, in what the DVLA hopes
OL,11,Fwill get drivers' attention to the
OL,12,Frisks of not paying their tax.
OL,14,FIt is not long before we find an
OL,15,Funtaxed vehicle parked in the road.
OL,16,FIts owner is overdue by several weeks
OL,17,Fand now they will have to pay at least
OL,18,F#100 just to have the clamp removed,
OL,19,Fon top of the tax they still owe.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FThe amount drivers pay for road tax
OL,7,Fvaries. Depending on the car's eco-
OL,8,Ffriendliness, it can cost anywhere
OL,9,Fbetween #10 and a few thousand pounds.
OL,10,FNew electric vehicles will pay very
OL,11,Flittle whereas old diesel vehicles
OL,12,Fwill pay much more.
OL,14,FIf you bought your car for more than
OL,15,F#40,000, there is an extra cost too
OL,16,Fknown as the luxury car tax.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FFrom 1 April 2026, the list price at
OL,7,Fwhich you pay the luxury car tax
OL,8,Fincreased to #50,000 for electric
OL,9,Fvehicles. Non-electric cars will still
OL,10,Fhave the same #40,000 threshold.
OL,12,FBack on patrol and we watch as a
OL,13,Fdifferent car parked on a Newport
OL,14,Fresidential street is lifted onto a
OL,15,Ftow-truck. Its owner appears to have
OL,16,Fignored the warnings on the clamp or
OL,17,Fin the post, which now means their car
OL,18,Fis taken to the DVLA's vehicle pound
OL,19,Fin the city.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FIt is a car park you never want to
OL,7,Fenter. On any given month, up to 900
OL,8,Fcars can be clamped by the team in
OL,9,FNewport and the pound can have around
OL,10,F100 cars in there at any one time.
OL,12,FMany vehicles are soon picked up, with
OL,13,Fthe owners paying an additional fine
OL,14,Ffor every day it is in the DVLA's
OL,15,Fpossession. The mix of cars is
OL,16,Fstriking. Some are so old, you wonder
OL,17,Fif their owners will decide they're
OL,18,Fnot worth paying the fine for, while
OL,19,Fothers are new and valuable vehicles.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FLast year the DVLA collected #110
OL,7,Fmillion from enforcement action, with
OL,8,Fthe money going back into the UK
OL,9,FTreasury to be spent on anything from
OL,10,Fdefence to policing.
OL,12,FThe DVLA says unpaid road tax can
OL,13,Foften be linked with wider
OL,14,Fcriminality. Cars that are left in the
OL,15,Fpound for over a week or two are
OL,16,Feither auctioned off, or scrapped
OL,17,Fdepending on their value.
OL,19,FClearances of cars that leave the
OL,20,Fpound for those reasons have been
OL,21,Ffound with weapons, cash and drugs.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FHowever for the vast majority of
OL,7,Fpeople, failing to pay road tax is an
OL,8,Fhonest albeit expensive mistake.
OL,10,FFor those unable to afford to pay
OL,11,Ftheir annual road tax up front, you
OL,12,Fcan choose to pay on the first of
OL,13,Fevery month or every six months. It is
OL,14,Fslightly cheaper to pay it all in a
OL,15,Flump sum by direct debit every year.
OL,17,FThe Pound and Transport Manager for
OL,18,FNewport, Claire Jones, said helping
OL,19,Fpeople who make mistakes with their
OL,20,Froad tax is an important part of their
OL,21,Fjob.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,F"I like to instill in my enforcement
OL,7,Fofficers that if a car's clamped and
OL,8,Fthey come across the confrontational
OL,9,Fperson, they understand how to
OL,10,Fapproach them and how to help them,"
OL,11,Fshe explained.
OL,13,FClaire said up to 85% of people who
OL,14,Fconfront their staff about the clamp
OL,15,Fare then calmed down when their
OL,16,Fofficers talk them through how to have
OL,17,Fthe clamp removed with payment or help
OL,18,Fthem through the payment line or doing
OL,19,Fonline. Many clamps are removed there
OL,20,Fand then.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778249472
OL,3,CWhat happens to the thousands of cars
OL,4,Cclamped every month in Wales?
OL,6,FShe added: "It's having a bit
OL,7,Fcompassion as well because you've got
OL,8,Fyour little old ladies or you have you
OL,9,Fmums with young children and the
OL,10,Fenforcement officers have to have that
OL,11,Fcompassion as well".
OL,13,FIf you drive a vehicle and you're
OL,14,Funsure if the tax is up to date, you
OL,15,Fcan enter your registration number on
OL,16,Fthe UK Government website.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
